root.markup_cdata:
This CDATA contains <tags> and &entities;
All markup is treated literally: <element attr="value"/>
Even quotes "double" and 'single' are literal

root.complex_cdata:
XML Example:
<?xml version="1.0"?>
<document>
  <title>Test Document</title>
  <content>
    This is content with <emphasis>markup</emphasis>
    And entities like &amp; &lt; &gt;
  </content>
</document>

JavaScript Example:
function test() {
  if (x < 5 && y > 0) {
    return "condition met";
  }
}

Regular expressions: /[a-zA-Z]+\d*/g
